<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,308,1780,1806]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">Remarks</emphasis>
. This is a rare species with no molecular data. 
<bibRefCitation author="Zinovjev, A. G." box="[828,1011,1780,1806]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="55 - 57" refId="ref81234" refString="Zinovjev, A. G. (1992) Geograficheskoe rasprostranenie pilil'shchikov roda Kelidoptera Konow (Hymenoptera, Pamphiliidae) i bozmozhnost' faunisticheskikh svyazej yuzhnogo Urala s Maloj Aziej. In: Nasekomye v Estestvennykh i Antropogennykh Biogeotsenozakh Urala, Materialy IV Soveshchaniya Entomologov Urala, Perm', 24 - 26 Marta 1992 g., pp. 55 - 57." type="journal article" year="1992">Zinovjev (1992)</bibRefCitation>
